profile:
We Design, Construct and Maintain outdoor spaces that leave you breathless.

We are Ontario's leading landscaping and construction company, based in Toronto. We pride ourselves in providing professional, accurate and friendly service. We always assure 100% satisfaction to every customer, with quality work that lasts - for years and years of enjoyment.

We will help you with individual design ideas, materials, location recommendations & anything else needed, to get your landscaping project started.

All work is performed in an ethical and patient - yet timely - manner. And the quality is proudly guaranteed for up to 5 years.

profile:
Welcome to Georgetown's favourite full-service pool supply, service, maintenance and installation company. We provide reliable water testing, repair and renovation services, spring openings, fall closings, weekly maintenance as well as supplying a complete line of high quality equipment and pool care products.
With a friendly and experienced staff , you can be sure we will get the job done and get it done right.
Serving Halton Hills since 2009, we've quickly become your trusted neighbourhood source for everything you need to keep your swimming season safe, easy and fun. Contact us today for more details on all of our products and services.
